channel.title: You can still view the old google
channel.description:
Kk well not really the old google but if you noticed they had moved the "Web Images Groups" ect. to the top of their webpage.. But if you go to : http://www.ggoogle.com/ Then you can use google without the Links at the top :)
(Notice the two "g"'s in http://www.ggoogle.com/)
